# Transitions ğŸ¬

Smoothly change property values over a given duration.

```css
.btn {
  background: blue;
  transition: background 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.btn:hover {
  background: red;
}
```

- `property`: What to animate (e.g., `all`, `color`)
- `duration`: How long (e.g., `0.5s`)
- `timing-function`: Speed curve (`linear`, `ease`, `ease-in`)

# Keyframes ğŸï¸

Create complex animations with steps.

```css
@keyframes slideIn {
  from { transform: translateX(-100%); }
  to { transform: translateX(0); }
}

.box {
  animation: slideIn 1s forwards;
}
```

You can use percentages too:
```css
@keyframes bounce {
  0% { top: 0; }
  50% { top: -20px; }
  100% { top: 0; }
}
```
